{"type":"assistant","uuid":"202603120222526e0c297364e84509","session_id":"7d08652e-4d6f-459a-a10d-c983fbe8d044","message":{"id":"202603120222526e0c297364e84509","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde23361b42110f51554db9459958","name":"Task","input":{"description":"PM creates spec/plan/tasks for F-001","prompt":"Read /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.codebuddy/agents/prizm-dev-team-pm.md for your role definition.\n\nFor feature F-001 (slug: 001-project-infrastructure-setup), complete all three planning steps in this single session:\n\n**Feature Description:**\n为 Telegram 管道模式建立统一的工程基线：明确配置分层、目录约定、日志与状态文件位置、脚本入口与错误码规范。该功能聚焦于让后续命令路由与 pipeline 控制能力有稳定的运行基础，并保持与现有 dev-pipeline 脚本兼容。\n\n范围包括：规范 feature-list / bug-fix-list 输入目录、规范 state 与 session 日志目录、统一启动参数解析、补全 TypeScript 迁移所需的基础构建与检查配置（不要求一次性迁移全部历史代码）。\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- 提供统一的配置加载与校验入口，缺失关键配置时返回可读错误信息\n- 定义并落地计划文件、状态文件、日志文件的标准目录结构与命名规则\n- 提供可复用的脚本入口封装，能够以一致参数调用现有 dev-pipeline 脚本\n- 基础构建与静态检查流程可运行，且不会破坏现有 Telegram 对话主流程\n\n**App Global Context:**\n- design_system: Telegram command UX with structured message templates\n- language: TypeScript\n- tech_stack: Node.js + Express + Telegraf + JSON state files + Shell/Python dev-pipeline\n- testing_strategy: Jest (unit + integration)\n\n**Instructions:**\n1. First read `.prizm-docs/root.prizm` to understand project context\n2. Run prizmkit.specify → generate `.prizmkit/specs/001-project-infrastructure-setup/spec.md` (concise, under 150 lines)\n3. Run prizmkit.plan → generate `.prizmkit/specs/001-project-infrastructure-setup/plan.md` (architecture, components, interface design, data model, testing strategy — all in one file)\n4. Run prizmkit.tasks → generate `.prizmkit/specs/001-project-infrastructure-setup/tasks.md` with `[ ]` checkboxes\n\nAll three files go under `.prizmkit/specs/001-project-infrastructure-setup/`.\n\nEnsure tasks follow the numbering convention: Setup(T-001~T-009) → Foundational(T-010~T-099) → User Stories(T-100+) → Polish(T-900+).","subagent_type":"prizm-dev-team-pm","team_name":"prizm-dev-team"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":36807,"output_tokens":676,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:23:02.958Z","_requestId":"678379debffb49b699e7d6685b86f8c3"}
