{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312022342fcf7c8e15dc3446d","session_id":"7d08652e-4d6f-459a-a10d-c983fbe8d044","message":{"id":"20260312022342fcf7c8e15dc3446d","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde23f50a3cc9b579799b47767099","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/001-project-infrastructure-setup/spec.md","content":"# F-001: Project Infrastructure Setup\n\n## Summary\n\n为 Telegram 管道模式建立统一的工程基线，确保后续命令路由与 pipeline 控制能力有稳定的运行基础。\n\n## User Stories\n\n### US-1: 统一配置加载与校验\n\n**As a** 系统开发者  \n**I want** 通过单一入口加载所有配置并在缺失关键配置时获得可读错误  \n**So that** 我可以快速定位配置问题而非遇到难以理解的运行时错误\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- AC-1.1: `loadPipelineInfraConfig()` 返回冻结的配置对象\n- AC-1.2: 缺失必需字段时抛出结构化错误（含 code、hint、field）\n- AC-1.3: 支持 ENV 与 CLI 参数覆盖，CLI 优先\n\n### US-2: 标准目录结构与命名规则\n\n**As a** 运维人员  \n**I want** 所有计划文件、状态文件、日志文件有统一的目录结构与命名规则  \n**So that** 我可以快速定位问题并执行运维操作\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- AC-2.1: feature specs 存放于 `.prizmkit/specs/{slug}/`\n- AC-2.2: feature state 存放于 `dev-pipeline/state/features/{F-NNN}/`\n- AC-2.3: session logs 存放于 `dev-pipeline/state/features/{F-NNN}/sessions/{sessionId}/logs/`\n- AC-2.4: daemon logs 存放于 `dev-pipeline/state/pipeline-daemon.log`\n\n### US-3: 脚本入口封装\n\n**As a** 控制层开发者  \n**I want** 通过统一的 JS 函数调用 dev-pipeline 脚本  \n**So that** 我可以在 Telegram handler 中可靠地执行 pipeline 操作\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- AC-3.1: `buildPipelineCommand()` 构造正确的脚本路径与参数\n- AC-3.2: `executePipelineCommand()` 执行脚本并返回标准化结果\n- AC-3.3: 支持 run/status/stop/logs/retry/reset 操作\n\n### US-4: TypeScript 构建与静态检查\n\n**As a** 项目维护者  \n**I want** 基础构建与静态检查流程可运行  \n**So that** 我可以在渐进迁移过程中保证代码质量\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- AC-4.1: `npm run typecheck` 成功执行且不破坏现有流程\n- AC-4.2: `npm run lint` 成功执行\n- AC-4.3: tsconfig.json 包含 pipeline-infra 与 pipeline-control-service\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n- 配置加载与校验 (`src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js`)\n- 路径策略模块 (`src/pipeline-infra/path-policy.js`)\n- 错误码定义 (`src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js`)\n- 脚本运行器 (`src/pipeline-infra/script-runner.js`)\n- Python 路径策略镜像 (`dev-pipeline/scripts/path_policy.py`)\n- TypeScript 配置 (`tsconfig.json`)\n- 单元测试覆盖\n\n### Out of Scope\n- 历史代码的完整 TypeScript 迁移\n- Telegram 命令路由（F-002）\n- 进程控制器高层 API（F-004）\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- 无外部依赖（基础设施功能）\n\n## Risks\n\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| 配置加载逻辑复杂导致难以调试 | 保持函数纯度，添加详细测试用例 |\n| Python/JS 路径策略不同步 | 建立兼容性测试确保行为一致 |\n| TypeScript 配置过于严格阻塞开发 | 初始 strict: false，渐进收紧 |\n\n## Non-Functional Requirements\n\n- **性能**: 配置加载在 10ms 内完成\n- **可维护性**: 每个模块单文件，函数长度 < 100 行\n- **测试覆盖**: 核心模块 > 90% 分支覆盖\n"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":37149,"output_tokens":942,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde23361b42110f51554db9459958","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:23:59.376Z","_requestId":"678379debffb49b699e7d6685b86f8c3"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"d31d245a-ac91-49b3-8efc-a09d0abbfadb","session_id":"7d08652e-4d6f-459a-a10d-c983fbe8d044","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde23f50a3cc9b579799b47767099","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully overwrote file: /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/001-project-infrastructure-setup/spec.md"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde23361b42110f51554db9459958","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:23:59.382Z","_requestId":"678379debffb49b699e7d6685b86f8c3"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"202603120223591c130f3dcfa94999","session_id":"7d08652e-4d6f-459a-a10d-c983fbe8d044","message":{"id":"202603120223591c130f3dcfa94999","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde2438bfc601538e0776dd423bd6","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/001-project-infrastructure-setup/plan.md","content":"# F-001: Technical Implementation Plan\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                        Entry Points                              │\n│  src/index.js → src/config.js → src/pipeline-infra/index.js    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    Configuration Layer                           │\n│  ┌─────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────┐                    │\n│  │ config-loader.js│◄───│  error-codes.js │                    │\n│  └────────┬────────┘    └─────────────────┘                    │\n│           │              ┌─────────────────┐                    │\n│           └─────────────►│  path-policy.js │                    │\n│                          └─────────────────┘                    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Execution Layer                              │\n│  ┌─────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ script-runner.js│───►│ dev-pipeline/*.sh + scripts/*.py│    │\n│  └─────────────────┘    └─────────────────────────────────┘    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      State Layer                                 │\n│  .prizmkit/specs/    dev-pipeline/state/    dev-pipeline/logs/ │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Component Design\n\n### C-1: config-loader.js (已实现)\n\n**Responsibility**: 加载并校验 pipeline 基础设施配置\n\n**Input**: `{ env?, argv?, cwd? }`\n\n**Output**: 冻结的配置对象\n\n**Key Functions**:\n- `loadPipelineInfraConfig(input?)` - 主入口\n- `toArgMap(argv)` - 解析 CLI 参数\n- `toAbsolutePath(raw, projectRoot)` - 路径解析\n- `parseInteger({ raw, field, min, code, hint })` - 整数解析\n\n### C-2: path-policy.js (已实现)\n\n**Responsibility**: 计算和验证 pipeline 相关路径\n\n**Key Functions**:\n- `computeFeatureSlug(featureId, title)` - 生成 slug\n- `resolveFeaturePaths(input)` - 解析 feature 相关路径\n- `resolveBugPaths(input)` - 解析 bugfix 相关路径\n- `resolveDaemonLogPaths(projectRoot)` - 解析 daemon 日志路径\n\n### C-3: error-codes.js (已实现)\n\n**Responsibility**: 定义并创建结构化错误\n\n**Constants**:\n- `CONFIG_MISSING` - 必需配置缺失\n- `CONFIG_INVALID` - 配置值无效\n- `PATH_INVALID` - 路径不合法\n- `SCRIPT_NOT_FOUND` - 脚本不存在\n- `EXEC_TIMEOUT` - 执行超时\n- `EXEC_FAILED` - 执行失败\n\n**Functions**:\n- `createInfraError(code, message, options?)` - 创建结构化错误\n- `isInfraErrorCode(code)` - 校验错误码\n\n### C-4: script-runner.js (已实现)\n\n**Responsibility**: 构建并执行 dev-pipeline 脚本命令\n\n**Key Functions**:\n- `buildPipelineCommand(req, config)` - 构建命令\n- `executePipelineCommand(req)` - 执行命令\n- `normalizePipelineResult(raw)` - 标准化结果\n\n### C-5: path_policy.py (已实现)\n\n**Responsibility**: Python 版本的路径策略，与 JS 保持行为一致\n\n**Key Functions**: 与 `path-policy.js` 镜像\n\n## Interface Design\n\n### I-1: PipelineInfraConfig\n\n```typescript\ninterface PipelineInfraConfig {\n  readonly projectRoot: string;\n  readonly pipelineDir: string;\n  readonly featureListPath: string;\n  readonly bugFixListPath: string;\n  readonly stateDir: string;\n  readonly bugfixStateDir: string;\n  readonly maxRetries: number;\n  readonly sessionTimeoutSec: number;\n  readonly heartbeatIntervalSec: number;\n  readonly aiCli: string;\n  readonly platform: 'codebuddy' | 'claude';\n}\n```\n\n### I-2: FeaturePaths\n\n```typescript\ninterface FeaturePaths {\n  readonly featureSlug: string;\n  readonly specsDir: string;\n  readonly sessionDir: string;\n  readonly sessionLog: string;\n  readonly sessionStatus: string;\n}\n```\n\n### I-3: PipelineCommandRequest\n\n```typescript\ninterface PipelineCommandRequest {\n  pipelineType: 'feature' | 'bugfix';\n  action: 'run' | 'status' | 'stop' | 'logs' | 'retry' | 'reset';\n  targetId?: string;\n  listPath?: string;\n  timeoutMs?: number;\n  envOverrides?: Record<string, string>;\n}\n```\n\n### I-4: PipelineCommandResult\n\n```typescript\ninterface PipelineCommandResult {\n  readonly ok: boolean;\n  readonly exitCode: number;\n  readonly stdout: string;\n  readonly stderr: string;\n  readonly normalizedStatus: 'success' | 'failed' | 'timed_out' | 'crashed';\n  readonly errorCode?: InfraErrorCode;\n}\n```\n\n### I-5: InfraError\n\n```typescript\ninterface InfraError {\n  readonly code: InfraErrorCode;\n  readonly message: string;\n  readonly hint?: string;\n  readonly context?: Record<string, unknown>;\n}\n```\n\n## Data Model\n\n### D-1: Directory Structure\n\n```\n{projectRoot}/\n├── .prizmkit/\n│   └── specs/\n│       └── {slug}/           # e.g., 001-project-infrastructure-setup/\n│           ├── spec.md\n│           ├── plan.md\n│           └── tasks.md\n├── dev-pipeline/\n│   ├── state/\n│   │   ├── pipeline.json\n│   │   ├── pipeline-daemon.log\n│   │   └── features/\n│   │       └── {F-NNN}/\n│   │           ├── status.json\n│   │           └── sessions/\n│   │               └── {sessionId}/\n│   │                   ├── session-status.json\n│   │                   └── logs/\n│   │                       ├── session.log\n│   │                       └── progress.json\n│   ├── bugfix-state/\n│   │   ├── pipeline-daemon.log\n│   │   └── bugs/\n│   │       └── {B-NNN}/\n│   │           └── sessions/\n│   │               └── {sessionId}/\n│   └── scripts/\n│       └── path_policy.py\n├── feature-list.json\n└── bug-fix-list.json\n```\n\n### D-2: Config Precedence\n\n```\nCLI Arguments (--project-root, --pipeline-dir, etc.)\n       │\n       ▼ (overrides)\nEnvironment Variables (PIPELINE_PROJECT_ROOT, PIPELINE_DIR, etc.)\n       │\n       ▼ (overrides)\nDefault Values (cwd, path.join(cwd, 'dev-pipeline'), etc.)\n```\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests (已实现)\n\n| Module | Test File | Coverage Target |\n|--------|-----------|-----------------|\n| error-codes.js | error-codes.test.js | 100% |\n| path-policy.js | path-policy.test.js | 95% |\n| config-loader.js | config-loader.test.js | 95% |\n| script-runner.js | script-runner.test.js | 90% |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Scenario | Test File | Purpose |\n|----------|-----------|---------|\n| Python-JS Path Parity | path-policy-python-compat.test.js | 确保 path_policy.py 与 path-policy.js 行为一致 |\n| Script Execution | python-script-integration.test.js | 验证脚本执行链路 |\n| Full Config Flow | config.test.js | 验证 config.js 集成 |\n\n### Test Commands\n\n```bash\nnpm run test                    # 运行所有测试\nnpm run typecheck               # TypeScript 类型检查\nnpm run lint                    # ESLint 检查\n```\n\n## User Story Mapping\n\n| User Story | Components | Key Files |\n|------------|------------|-----------|\n| US-1: 统一配置加载与校验 | C-1, C-3 | config-loader.js, error-codes.js |\n| US-2: 标准目录结构 | C-2, C-5 | path-policy.js, path_policy.py |\n| US-3: 脚本入口封装 | C-4 | script-runner.js |\n| US-4: TypeScript 构建 | - | tsconfig.json |\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### N-1: 冻结对象策略\n\n所有配置对象使用 `Object.freeze()` 返回，防止意外修改：\n```javascript\nreturn Object.freeze({\n  projectRoot,\n  pipelineDir,\n  // ...\n});\n```\n\n### N-2: 错误处理模式\n\n错误包含 `code`、`hint`、`context` 三要素：\n```javascript\nthrow {\n  code: 'CONFIG_MISSING',\n  message: 'projectRoot is required',\n  hint: 'Set --project-root or PIPELINE_PROJECT_ROOT',\n  context: { field: 'projectRoot' }\n};\n```\n\n### N-3: TypeScript 渐进迁移\n\n当前配置：\n- `strict: false` - 允许宽松类型\n- `allowJs: true`, `checkJs: true` - 检查 JS 文件\n- 仅包含 `src/pipeline-infra/**/*.js` 和 `src/services/pipeline-control-service.js`\n\n后续收紧策略：\n1. 为核心文件添加 JSDoc 类型注解\n2. 逐步扩展 `include` 范围\n3. 启用 `strict: true`\n\n## Risks & Mitigations\n\n| Risk | Impact | Likelihood | Mitigation |\n|------|--------|------------|------------|\n| 配置项增加导致维护负担 | Medium | Medium | 使用 Zod schema 统一校验 |\n| Python/JS 行为不一致 | High | Low | 兼容性测试 + 共享测试用例 |\n| 新增依赖导致构建变慢 | Low | Low | 保持最小依赖 |\n"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":38129,"output_tokens":2324,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde23361b42110f51554db9459958","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:24:38.642Z","_requestId":"678379debffb49b699e7d6685b86f8c3"}
