-26)\n\n**Impact:** Spec compliance failure - error object shape doesn't match specification\n\n**Fix Suggestion:**\nOption A: Add `field` property to InfraError interface in plan.md and implementation\nOption B: Update AC-1.2 to: \"含 code、hint，字段信息在 context.field 中\"\n\n---\n\n#### [H-3] Scope Coverage Gap: `path_policy.py` Not Tracked\n\n**Location:**\n- spec.md: In Scope section (line 61)\n- plan.md: File Change Summary (lines 294-306)\n- tasks.md: No dedicated task\n\n**Issue:**\n- spec.md lists \"Python 路径策略镜像 (`dev-pipeline/scripts/path_policy.py`)\" in In Scope\n- plan.md File Change Summary does not include this file\n- tasks.md has T-102 (compatibility test) but no task to verify the Python file itself\n- File exists at `/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/dev-pipeline/scripts/path_policy.py`\n\n**Impact:** Incomplete scope tracking, risk of missing verification\n\n**Fix Suggestion:**\nEither:\n- Remove from spec.md In Scope (if already implemented and stable), OR\n- Add to plan.md File Change Summary as \"已实现 | 无需修改\"\n- Add task T-016: \"Verify path_policy.py implementation\"\n\n---\n\n### MEDIUM Severity\n\n#### [M-1] NFR Performance Not Tested\n\n**Location:**\n- spec.md: NFR section (line 84)\n- tasks.md: No matching test task\n\n**Issue:**\n- NFR: 配置加载在 10ms 内完成\n- No task verifies this performance requirement\n\n**Fix Suggestion:**\nAdd test task to verify performance constraint, or document as \"covered by implementation\" with rationale\n\n---\n\n#### [M-2] AC-4.3 Verification Gap\n\n**Location:**\n- spec.md: AC-4.3 (line 52)\n- tasks.md: T-002 (lines 12-17)\n\n**Issue:**\n- AC-4.3: tsconfig.json 包含 pipeline-infra 与 pipeline-control-service\n- T-002 acceptance: \"`npm run typecheck` 通过\"\n- Typecheck passing does not guarantee specific directories are included\n\n**Fix Suggestion:**\nExpand T-002 acceptance criteria: \"tsconfig.json explicitly includes src/pipeline-infra/**/*.js and src/services/pipeline-control-service.js\"\n\n---\n\n### LOW Severity\n\n#### [L-1] NFR Test Coverage Not Verified\n\n**Location:**\n- spec.md: NFR section (line 86)\n- tasks.md: No coverage verification task\n\n**Issue:**\n- NFR: 核心模块 > 90% 分支覆盖\n- No task measures or verifies coverage percentage\n\n**Fix Suggestion:**\nAdd T-108: \"Verify test coverage meets threshold\" with acceptance: \"npm run test:coverage shows >90% for pipeline-infra modules\"\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Severity | Count | Resolution |\n|----------|-------|------------|\n| CRITICAL | 0 | - |\n| HIGH | 3 | Requires PM fix |\n| MEDIUM | 2 | Recommended fix |\n| LOW | 1 | Optional |\n\n---\n\n## Verdict\n\n### **PASS_WITH_WARNINGS**\n\n**Rationale:**\n- No CRITICAL issues found\n- 3 HIGH issues require PM attention before implementation\n- All HIGH issues have clear fix suggestions\n- Core document structure is sound\n\n**Required Actions for PM:**\n\n1. **H-1**: Document `buildPipelineCommand` interface in plan.md\n2. **H-2**: Resolve `field` property discrepancy between spec.md and plan.md\n3. **H-3**: Clarify `path_policy.py` scope status\n\n**Optional Improvements:**\n- M-1: Add performance test task\n- M-2: Expand T-002 acceptance criteria\n- L-1: Add coverage verification task\n\n---\n\n## COMPLETION_SIGNAL\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  PHASE 4: CROSS-DOCUMENT CONSISTENCY ANALYSIS - COMPLETE   │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  Feature:     F-001 (001-project-infrastructure-setup)      │\n│  Verdict:     PASS_WITH_WARNINGS                            │\n│  Critical:    0                                             │\n│  High:        3 (requires PM fix)                          │\n│  Medium:      2 (recommended)                               │\n│  Low:         1 (optional)                                  │\n│                                                             │\n│  Status:      Ready for implementation after PM addresses   │\n│               HIGH severity findings  