{"type":"user","uuid":"66a69b14-b849-49ff-94cc-bdacc43aa39f","session_id":"7d08652e-4d6f-459a-a10d-c983fbe8d044","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde28ec4b54122e064219bb6436d4","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-001: Technical Implementation Plan\n   2→\n   3→## Architecture Overview\n   4→\n   5→```\n   6→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n   7→│                        Entry Points                              │\n   8→├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n   9→│  src/index.js → HTTP Server + Telegram Bot                      │\n  10→└───────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘\n  11→                            │\n  12→┌───────────────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────┐\n  13→│                      Configuration Layer                         │\n  14→├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n  15→│  src/config.js ─────────────────────────────────────────────────│\n  16→│  ├─ env parsing (zod schema)                                    │\n  17→│  ├─ pipelineInfra ← src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js         │\n  18→│  └─ daemonLogPaths ← src/pipeline-infra/path-policy.js          │\n  19→└───────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘\n  20→                            │\n  21→┌───────────────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────┐\n  22→│                      Service Layer                               │\n  23→├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n  24→│  src/services/pipeline-control-service.js                       │\n  25→│  ├─ startPipeline(params)                                       │\n  26→│  ├─ getPipelineStatus(params)                                   │\n  27→│  ├─ stopPipeline(params)                                        │\n  28→│  ├─ retryTarget(params)                                         │\n  29→│  ├─ getPipelineLogs(params)                                     │\n  30→│  └─ resetTarget(params)                                         │\n  31→└───────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘\n  32→                            │\n  33→┌───────────────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────┐\n  34→│                    Infrastructure Layer                          │\n  35→├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n  36→│  src/pipeline-infra/                                            │\n  37→│  ├─ config-loader.js    (配置加载与校验)                         │\n  38→│  ├─ path-policy.js      (路径解析与安全校验)                     │\n  39→│  ├─ script-runner.js    (脚本执行封装)                           │\n  40→│  └─ error-codes.js      (错误码定义)                            │\n  41→└───────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘\n  42→                            │\n  43→┌───────────────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────┐\n  44→│                    External Scripts                              │\n  45→├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n  46→│  dev-pipeline/run.sh, run-bugfix.sh, retry-*.sh, reset-*.sh    │\n  47→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  48→```\n  49→\n  50→## Component Design\n  51→\n  52→### 1. config-loader.js\n  53→\n  54→**职责:** 从环境变量和命令行参数加载 pipeline 基础设施配置\n  55→\n  56→**输入:**\n  57→```typescript\n  58→interface LoadPipelineInfraConfigInput {\n  59→  env?: Record<string, string>;\n  60→  argv?: string[];\n  61→  cwd?: string;\n  62→}\n  63→```\n  64→\n  65→**输出:**\n  66→```typescript\n  67→interface PipelineInfraConfig {\n  68→  projectRoot: string;       // 项目根目录\n  69→  pipelineDir: string;       // dev-pipeline 目录\n  70→  featureListPath: string;   // feature-list.json 路径\n  71→  bugFixListPath: string;    // bug-fix-list.json 路径\n  72→  stateDir: string;          // dev-pipeline/state\n  73→  bugfixStateDir: string;    // dev-pipeline/bugfix-state\n  74→  maxRetries: number;        // 最大重试次数\n  75→  sessionTimeoutSec: number; // 会话超时（秒）\n  76→  heartbeatIntervalSec: number;\n  77→  aiCli: string;             // AI CLI 命令\n  78→  platform: 'codebuddy' | 'claude';\n  79→}\n  80→```\n  81→\n  82→### 2. path-policy.js\n  83→\n  84→**职责:** 解析 feature/bug/session 路径，防止路径穿越攻击\n  85→\n  86→**接口:**\n  87→```typescript\n  88→// 已实现\n  89→function computeFeatureSlug(featureId: string, title: string): string;\n  90→function resolveFeaturePaths(input: {\n  91→  projectRoot: string;\n  92→  featureId: string;\n  93→  sessionId: string;\n  94→  title?: string;\n  95→}): {\n  96→  featureSlug: string;\n  97→  specsDir: string;\n  98→  sessionDir: string;\n  99→  sessionLog: string;\n 100→  sessionStatus: string;\n 101→};\n 102→function resolveBugPaths(input: {\n 103→  projectRoot: string;\n 104→  bugId: string;\n 105→  sessionId: string;\n 106→}): {\n 107→  bugDir: string;\n 108→  sessionDir: string;\n 109→  sessionLog: string;\n 110→  sessionStatus: string;\n 111→};\n 112→function resolveDaemonLogPaths(projectRoot: string): {\n 113→  featureDaemonLog: string;\n 114→  bugfixDaemonLog: string;\n 115→};\n 116→```\n 117→\n 118→**安全约束:**\n 119→- `SAFE_SEGMENT_PATTERN = /^[A-Za-z0-9._-]+$/`\n 120→- 拒绝包含 `..` 的路径段\n 121→- 所有路径最终通过 `path.resolve()` 规范化\n 122→\n 123→### 3. error-codes.js\n 124→\n 125→**职责:** 定义统一的错误码和错误对象创建函数\n 126→\n 127→**错误码:**\n 128→```typescript\n 129→const INFRA_ERROR_CODES = {\n 130→  CONFIG_MISSING: 'CONFIG_MISSING',   // 配置缺失\n 131→  CONFIG_INVALID: 'CONFIG_INVALID',   // 配置无效\n 132→  PATH_INVALID: 'PATH_INVALID',       // 路径无效\n 133→  SCRIPT_NOT_FOUND: 'SCRIPT_NOT_FOUND', // 脚本未找到\n 134→  EXEC_TIMEOUT: 'EXEC_TIMEOUT',       // 执行超时\n 135→  EXEC_FAILED: 'EXEC_FAILED'          // 执行失败\n 136→} as const;\n 137→```\n 138→\n 139→**错误对象:**\n 140→```typescript\n 141→interface InfraError {\n 142→  code: InfraErrorCode;\n 143→  message: string;\n 144→  hint?: string;\n 145→  context?: Record<string, unknown>;\n 146→}\n 147→```\n 148→\n 149→### 4. script-runner.js\n 150→\n 151→**职责:** 封装 dev-pipeline 脚本执行\n 152→\n 153→**接口:**\n 154→```typescript\n 155→interface ExecuteRequest {\n 156→  pipelineType: 'feature' | 'bugfix';\n 157→  action: 'run' | 'status' | 'stop' | 'retry' | 'logs' | 'reset';\n 158→  targetId?: string;         // F-001, B-001\n 159→  listPath?: string;         // 覆盖默认 list 路径\n 160→  envOverrides?: Record<string, string>;\n 161→  timeoutMs?: number;\n 162→}\n 163→\n 164→interface ExecuteResult {\n 165→  success: boolean;\n 166→  stdout: string;\n 167→  stderr: string;\n 168→  exitCode: number;\n 169→  durationMs: number;\n 170→}\n 171→\n 172→interface BuildCommandResult {\n 173→  scriptPath: string;\n 174→  args: string[];\n 175→  env: Record<string, string>;\n 176→}\n 177→\n 178→// 构造脚本路径与参数 (AC-3.1)\n 179→function buildPipelineCommand(request: ExecuteRequest): BuildCommandResult;\n 180→\n 181→// 执行脚本并返回标准化结果 (AC-3.2)\n 182→async function executePipelineCommand(request: ExecuteRequest): Promise<ExecuteResult>;\n 183→```\n 184→\n 185→**buildPipelineCommand() 脚本映射 (AC-3.1):**\n 186→| action | pipelineType | 脚本路径 | 参数 |\n 187→|--------|--------------|----------|------|\n 188→| run | feature | dev-pipeline/run.sh | --target {targetId} --list {listPath} |\n 189→| run | bugfix | dev-pipeline/run-bugfix.sh | --target {targetId} --list {listPath} |\n 190→| status | both | (内部读取 state JSON) | N/A |\n 191→| stop | both | (kill daemon PID) | N/A |\n 192→| retry | feature | dev-pipeline/retry-feature.sh | --target {targetId} |\n 193→| retry | bugfix | dev-pipeline/retry-bug.sh | --target {targetId} |\n 194→| logs | both | (读取 daemon log 文件) | N/A |\n 195→| reset | feature | dev-pipeline/reset-feature.sh | --target {targetId} |\n 196→\n 197→**executePipelineCommand() 执行逻辑 (AC-3.2):**\n 198→1. 调用 `buildPipelineCommand()` 获取脚本路径和参数\n 199→2. spawn 子进程执行脚本\n 200→3. 捕获 stdout/stderr，处理超时\n 201→4. 返回标准化 ExecuteResult\n 202→\n 203→### 5. pipeline-control-service.js\n 204→\n 205→**职责:** 提供高层 API 供 HTTP/Telegram 路由调用\n 206→\n 207→**接口:**\n 208→```typescript\n 209→interface PipelineControlService {\n 210→  startPipeline(params: ServiceParams): Promise<ServiceResult>;\n 211→  getPipelineStatus(params: ServiceParams): Promise<ServiceResult>;\n 212→  stopPipeline(params: ServiceParams): Promise<ServiceResult>;\n 213→  retryTarget(params: ServiceParams): Promise<ServiceResult>;\n 214→  getPipelineLogs(params: ServiceParams): Promise<ServiceResult>;\n 215→  resetTarget(params: ServiceParams): Promise<ServiceResult>;\n 216→}\n 217→\n 218→interface ServiceParams {\n 219→  pipelineType?: 'feature' | 'bugfix';\n 220→  targetId?: string;\n 221→  listPath?: string;\n 222→  envOverrides?: Record<string, string>;\n 223→  timeoutMs?: number;\n 224→}\n 225→\n 226→interface ServiceResult {\n 227→  ok: boolean;\n 228→  data?: unknown;\n 229→  error?: InfraError;\n 230→}\n 231→```\n 232→\n 233→## Data Model\n 234→\n 235→### Directory Structure\n 236→\n 237→```\n 238→project-root/\n 239→├── .prizmkit/\n 240→│   └── specs/\n 241→│       └── 001-feature-slug/\n 242→│           ├── spec.md\n 243→│           ├── plan.md\n 244→│           └── tasks.md\n 245→├── dev-pipeline/\n 246→│   ├── state/\n 247→│   │   ├── pipeline-daemon.log\n 248→│   │   └── features/\n 249→│   │       └── F-001/\n 250→│   │           └── sessions/\n 251→│   │               └── sess-001/\n 252→│   │                   ├── logs/\n 253→│   │                   │   └── session.log\n 254→│   │                   └── session-status.json\n 255→│   └── bugfix-state/\n 256→│       ├── pipeline-daemon.log\n 257→│       └── bugs/\n 258→│           └── B-001/\n 259→│               └── sessions/\n 260→│                   └── sess-001/\n 261→│                       ├── logs/\n 262→│                       │   └── session.log\n 263→│                       └── session-status.json\n 264→├── feature-list.json\n 265→└── bug-fix-list.json\n 266→```\n 267→\n 268→### session-status.json Schema\n 269→\n 270→```json\n 271→{\n 272→  \"targetId\": \"F-001\",\n 273→  \"sessionId\": \"sess-001\",\n 274→  \"status\": \"running|completed|failed|timeout\",\n 275→  \"startedAt\": \"2024-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n 276→  \"completedAt\": null,\n 277→  \"exitCode\": null,\n 278→  \"retries\": 0\n 279→}\n 280→```\n 281→\n 282→## Testing Strategy\n 283→\n 284→### Unit Tests\n 285→\n 286→| 模块 | 测试文件 | 覆盖目标 |\n 287→|------|----------|----------|\n 288→| config-loader.js | tests/pipeline-infra/config-loader.test.js | 配置解析、默认值、错误处理 |\n 289→| path-policy.js | tests/pipeline-infra/path-policy.test.js | 路径解析、安全校验 |\n 290→| error-codes.js | tests/pipeline-infra/error-codes.test.js | 错误码创建、验证 |\n 291→| script-runner.js | tests/pipeline-infra/script-runner.test.js | 脚本执行、超时、错误处理 |\n 292→| pipeline-control-service.js | tests/services/pipeline-control-service.test.js | API 契约 |\n 293→\n 294→### Integration Tests\n 295→\n 296→| 场景 | 测试文件 |\n 297→|------|----------|\n 298→| Python 路径策略兼容性 | tests/pipeline-infra/path-policy-python-compat.test.js |\n 299→| 端到端用户故事 | tests/integration/f001-user-stories.integration.test.js |\n 300→\n 301→### Test Commands\n 302→\n 303→```bash\n 304→npm test                           # 运行所有测试\n 305→npm test -- tests/pipeline-infra/  # 仅运行 pipeline-infra 测试\n 306→npm run typecheck                  # TypeScript 类型检查\n 307→npm run lint                       # ESLint 检查\n 308→```\n 309→\n 310→## File Change Summary\n 311→\n 312→| 文件 | 状态 | 说明 |\n 313→|------|------|------|\n 314→| src/config.js | 修改 | 整合 pipelineInfra 配置 |\n 315→| src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js | 已实现 | 无需修改 |\n 316→| src/pipeline-infra/path-policy.js | 已实现 | 无需修改 |\n 317→| src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js | 已实现 | 无需修改 |\n 318→| src/pipeline-infra/script-runner.js | 已实现 | 无需修改 |\n 319→| src/services/pipeline-control-service.js | 已实现 | 无需修改 |\n 320→| tsconfig.json | 修改 | 扩展覆盖范围 |\n 321→| tests/**/*.test.js | 新增/修改 | 测试覆盖 |\n 322→\n 323→## Risk Mitigation\n 324→\n 325→| 风险 | 缓解措施 |\n 326→|------|----------|\n 327→| dev-pipeline 脚本变更 | 通过 `script-runner.js` 抽象层隔离，脚本路径可配置 |\n 328→| TypeScript 配置冲突 | 使用 `allowJs: true` 和 `checkJs: true`，增量迁移 |\n 329→| Python 路径策略不一致 | `path-policy-python-compat.test.js` 确保双向兼容 |\n 330→\n 331→## Success Criteria\n 332→\n 333→- [x] `npm run typecheck` 通过\n 334→- [x] `npm run lint` 通过\n 335→- [x] `npm test` 全部通过\n 336→- [x] 现有 Telegram 对话功能正常\n 337→- [x] 文档更新至 `.prizm-docs/`\n 338→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde28643f6482d5bec0578db0859f","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:29:10.451Z","_requestId":"678379debffb49b699e7d6685b86f8c3"}
